{"tid":2245244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[還原水]老母俾人呃咗","createTime":"2020-10-16T05:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T06:19:29.000Z","uid":354817,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3f00d1716e37f669d4d79d110b19de485c6632","tid":2245244,"uid":354817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:30:30.000Z","msg":"近排老母買咗部還原水機 原本都唔為意 因為啲水的確係過濾咗冇咗浸味 我都因此飲多咗水 但係老母係屋企係咁打電話sell啲朋友買 仲話可以分傭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母層壓式銷售聽完先知唔對路 問返先知原來買咗三萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返個背景先 小弟我係單親家庭 早排阿媽帶咗個男人上嚟仲同我介紹  後尾發覺就係呢條友賣水機 懷疑老母俾人呃咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們我應該點做 呢個情況可唔可以報警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f2bf48eaca9005bc318ff289f8f1029f6208d7","tid":2245244,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"喺連登講報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f034aca783be545bd552244bcca7cdff7526fa","tid":2245244,"uid":354817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92f2bf48eaca9005bc318ff289f8f1029f6208d7","tid":2245244,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"喺連登講報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"如果唔係應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵區議員幫手？"},{"pid":"b426cc9418aafc4c49494229f3de9dc4723369bd","tid":2245244,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2f034aca783be545bd552244bcca7cdff7526fa","tid":2245244,"uid":354817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92f2bf48eaca9005bc318ff289f8f1029f6208d7","tid":2245244,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"喺連登講報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.g